{{Nihongo|'''Japan Football Hall of Fame'''|日本サッカー殿堂}} is housed at the [[Japan Football Museum]] ([[:ja:日本サッカーミュージアム]]), in JFA House in [[Bunkyo]], [[Tokyo]]. The Hall aims to celebrate the achievements of the all-time top Japanese footballing players, managers and other person who have become significant figures in the history of the Japanese game.
