astech.com/genrel/111008aaa.html|title=Texas Tech Signs Exclusive Outfitter Deal With Under Armour|work=Texas Tech University Athletics|accessdate=October 29, 2012| date = November 10, 2008}}</ref><!--Texas Tech women's basketball uses "Lady Raiders", but all other women's teams use "Red Raiders".--> *{{flagicon|California}} [[UCLA Bruins]]<ref>http://espn.go.com/college-football/story/_/id/15697609/ucla-bruins-announce-15-year-280-million-deal-armour</ref> *{{flagicon|Utah}} [[Utah Utes]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/Daily/Issues/2008/03/Issue-130/Sponsorships-Advertising-Marketing/Under-Armour-Signs-Deal-With-Univ-Of-Utah-Football.aspx|title=Under Armour Signs Deal With Univ. Of Utah Football|publisher=|accessdate=2 May 2015}}</ref> *{{flagicon|Wisconsin}} [[Wisconsin Badgers]]<ref>http://espn.go.com/college-sports/story/_/id/13845985/under-armour-signs-10-year-96m-deal-wisconsin-badgers</ref> {{div col end}}
