'''Stade de la Réunification''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Douala]], [[Cameroon]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as a home ground of [[Union Douala]]. The stadium holds 30,000 people and was built in 1972.

